      "title": "Блок \"Почему выбирают нас\"?",
      "text": "<h3 class=\"special-heading text-center\">Why<span class=\"text-gradient\">Choose</span> Us</h3>\r\n                    <p class=\"fs-20 color-dark\">The Car Repair Appointment</p>\r\n                    <div class=\"divider-60 d-none d-lg-block\"></div>\r\n                    <p>Autospa Hand Wash is an eco-friendly, hand car wash and detailing service based in Portland. Our company was founded back in 2005 by a team of experts with\r\n                        more then 10 years of professional car wash experience.</p>\r\n                    <p>Our goal is to provide our customers with the friendliest, most convenient hand car wash experience possible. We use the most modern and up-to-date.</p>\r\n                    <div class=\"row text-left c-gutter-60\">\r\n                        <div class=\"divider-35\"></div>\r\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-box text-center\">\r\n                                <div class=\"icon-styled color-main2 fs-40\">\r\n                                    <i class=\"ico-mechanic\"></i>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <p>\r\n                                    We offer multiple services at a great value\r\n                                </p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-box text-center\">\r\n                                <div class=\"icon-styled color-main2 fs-40\">\r\n                                    <i class=\"ico-car-wash\"></i>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <p>\r\n                                    Multiple car wash locations throughout Portland\r\n                                </p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"col-md-4\">\r\n                            <div class=\"icon-box text-center\">\r\n                                <div class=\"icon-styled color-main2 fs-40\">\r\n                                    <i class=\"ico-painting\"></i>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <p>\r\n                                    Biodegradable and eco-friendly products\r\n                                </p>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    <div class=\"divider-33 d-none d-lg-block\"></div>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-small btn-maincolor\">Read more</a> <span class=\"color-dark m-25\">or</span> <a href=\"#\"\r\n                                                                                                                                 class=\"btn btn-small btn-outline-maincolor\">Get\r\n                        Started</a>\r\n                    </div>"
